Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:04.30,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We really did it right this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:07.30,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Akechi's character turned out really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:10.34,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,He makes a good rival. That improves the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.46,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be boring without Eiji and Iwase.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:15.68,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what helped us along.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:19.08,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Shujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:21.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,This time we'll definitely do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:25.08,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if we don't win, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:27.04,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll just start something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:29.68,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:32.18,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Did we manage to beat {\i1}+Natural?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.58,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,T-this is Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.82,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You're in 4th. You passed {\i1}+Natural!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:38.72,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:40.22,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:40.90,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:42.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We passed them right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:45.58,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crow{\i0} in 3rd place was only 2 votes ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:47.98,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I meant by "too bad."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:49.06,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Two votes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:50.76,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's really close!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:52.26,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:54.80,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.02,0:01:00.06,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't beat {\i1}Crow,{\i0} but we still passed {\i1}+Natural.{\i0} We won't be canceled, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.28,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's the chief editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:04.28,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:05.56,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Sasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:07.80,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for always helping us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:11.16,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I said that I didn't think you\Ncould beat Niizuma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:13.28,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a bit rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:19.06,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,N-no. You only said it to\Nmotivate us to do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.78,0:01:21.64,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}PCP{\i0} is a popular manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:24.02,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't cancel something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.32,0:01:26.44,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi-kun. You've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:30.32,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Please continue improving {\i1}Jack{\i0} with {\i1}PCP.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:32.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:52.38,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Hey, if I could be with you right now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:02:01.72,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Then I could keep my voice from fading
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:08.44,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,The goals I've set for myself seem too high to reach,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:12.90,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,and I feel like I've lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:22.49,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,I'm relying on a broken compass and hiding in someone's shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:33.84,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,If we keep letting go of what we have to find something else,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:43.93,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1100)}then I'm convinced we can never grow up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:49.77,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1100)}Never
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:54.44,BakumanTitle,title,0,0,0,,Margin and Pitfall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:57.06,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,So, next subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.46,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,My superiors told me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:04.26,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,People can get tired of a collaboration pretty quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:06.02,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}Crow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.24,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:12.04,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,PCP could only do well at the end of the series.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:13.52,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll overtake them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:14.94,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.48,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:19.96,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried you might be\Nupset by losing to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:23.72,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Upset? Actually, I'm even more motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.34,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.60,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:29.40,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:32.48,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay here and think for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:33.84,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.14,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:40.76,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like more coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:54.28,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,5th place was {\i1}Ally of Justice.{\i0}\N7th place was {\i1}Road Racer Giri.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:58.84,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Below that it's a close battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:01.22,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But PCP got 4th place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.42,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:04.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Takahama-san and Fukuda-san put in a lot of effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:07.38,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't let our guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:08.14,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:11.64,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best to stay ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:13.28,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.02,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:17.62,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.72,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:21.44,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.74,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,He wants to have a meeting tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:25.82,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? We haven't finished the manuscript yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:30.34,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,He said something about really good news for {\i1}PCP.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.48,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Good news...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.82,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be an anime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.18,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I-it's a bit too soon for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:38.88,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.68,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Our manga is popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.82,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,An anime is what we've dreamed about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:45.92,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:48.92,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Drama CD?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.18,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:54.08,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the situation, so I thought you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.80,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:58.32,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Aren't you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:00.66,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,No, of course we're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:06.54,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But... {\i1}Crow{\i0} and the others each got\Nanimes. We're just getting a drama CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:11.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of the subject, it's pretty\Neasy for {\i1}PCP{\i0} to get a drama CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:15.06,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We've only been going for six\Nmonths, so this is pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:16.76,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:18.24,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We definitely want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:22.84,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,They don't want to spoil the characters,\Nso it will be an original story line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.84,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me know if you have any requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:27.02,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Voice actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:29.46,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Specifically for the role of Annojo Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:33.24,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I name the voice\Nactor that I want for that role?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:35.64,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly the kind of request I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:38.36,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Just let me know who...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.66,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who does the voice on the drama CD...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:44.28,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,When we get an anime, will that person still do the voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:45.84,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:48.76,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Mashiro-kun, we aren't discussing an anime right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.84,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah... Sorry! It's a bit too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:54.26,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But if we do eventually get an anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:59.10,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as the drama CD does\Nwell and you do get an anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:02.44,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,the chances of keeping the\Nsame voice actor are high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:06.50,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it! It was a good idea to stop\Nher from doing the +Natural role.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:09.28,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, who did you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.38,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Azuki Miho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:15.08,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Azuki Miho-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.60,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry. I don't think I know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:22.32,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine! She's a talented\Nand dedicated voice actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.54,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,O-okay. I'll pass that along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:29.70,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's going to follow the creators'\Nwishes as closely as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,If I get Azuki onto the drama CD...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:37.42,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost there. PCP will definitely get an anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:41.08,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard about a drama CD opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:44.84,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shonen Jack's{\i0} {\i1}PCP{\i0} manga series. For the main heroine...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.14,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Annojo Mai. Have you heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.62,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:51.28,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,The creators requested you for the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.24,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:52.88,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:56.32,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely do it! Please let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:08.61,BakumanText,,0,0,0,,{\an5\c&H545454&\fs44\3c&HF0F0F0&\frz347.5\move(624,424,622,274,23,6404)}I  heard  that  Ashirogi-sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:08.61,BakumanText,,0,0,0,,{\an5\c&H545454&\fs44\3c&HF0F0F0&\frz347.5\move(594,470,596,322,23,6404)}wanted me to be Annojo Mai
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:08.61,BakumanText,,0,0,0,,{\an5\c&H545454&\fs44\3c&HF0F0F0&\frz347.5\move(560,518,562,368,23,6404)}on  the  P C P  drama  CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:08.61,BakumanText,,0,0,0,,{\an5\c&H545454&\fs44\3c&HF0F0F0&\frz347.5\move(470,552,472,400,23,6404)}I  was  so  happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:08.60,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that Ashirogi-sensei wanted me\Nto be Annojo Mai on the {\i1}PCP{\i0} drama CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:10.16,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:15.83,BakumanText,,0,0,0,,{\fs44\c&H3A403D&\3c&HE6EEEB&\move(514,404,516,226,28,3990)}Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:15.83,BakumanText,,0,0,0,,{\fs44\c&H3A403D&\3c&HE6EEEB&\move(540,468,540,292,28,3990)}"Ashirogi-sensei"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:15.83,BakumanText,,0,0,0,,{\fs44\c&H3A403D&\3c&HE6EEEB&\move(584,534,584,358,28,3990)}that has a nice ring to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:15.82,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations! "Ashirogi-sensei"... that has a nice ring to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:22.71,BakumanText,,0,0,0,,{\fs44\c&H565656&\3c&HF6F6F6&\pos(426,324)\frz347.8}Yeah !
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:22.71,BakumanText,,0,0,0,,{\fs44\c&H565656&\3c&HF6F6F6&\frz347.8\pos(600,416)}Ever since I started reading
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:22.71,BakumanText,,0,0,0,,{\fs44\c&H565656&\3c&HF6F6F6&\frz347.8\pos(486,444)}Ashirog-sensei's
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:22.71,BakumanText,,0,0,0,,{\fs44\c&H565656&\3c&HF6F6F6&\frz347.8\pos(542,510)}manga, I thought so too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:24.62,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Ever since I started reading\NAshirogi-sensei's manga, I thought so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:25.96,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:29.16,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something good happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:33.08,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh... {\i1}PCP{\i0} is getting a drama CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:35.38,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,EH?! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:36.58,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.52,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,A drama CD?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:41.42,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,How well do you think that fits with the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:46.20,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Since we work on the manga,\Nwe want it to turn out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:48.40,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,More of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:53.20,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Moriya-san, you're always working on\Nyour own storyboard in your free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:56.50,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike you, I want to get serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.58,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,What's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:03.02,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We may be coworkers, but I can't tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:05.72,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's important for other people to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.46,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not drawing something\Nof your own, Shiratori-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.98,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Is that not okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:14.80,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:16.74,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But that seems like a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:19.62,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I like drawing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:24.14,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't know what to write about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:28.32,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,, Just draw and write about\Nsomething that you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.08,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Something that I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:35.02,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:39.98,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm home, Peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:41.82,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You're home early, Shun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:45.38,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We're about to have dinner. Will you join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:47.70,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:52.14,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Shun, you should work for dad's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:55.58,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm... not interested in cosmetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:57.70,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I like drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:01.96,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,If you were an artist, that would be one thing. But a manga artist's helper...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:07.80,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Saiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:08.68,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:10.40,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:14.18,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I hardly ever see you on the way to the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.94,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We used to always go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.92,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay on time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:19.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.72,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm used to drawing PCP now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.72,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I can spare some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:27.44,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember when we came here in middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:30.60,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought we knew everything back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.52,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Middle schoolers are all like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:36.28,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,And in the first summer of high\Nschool you kissed Kaya-chan here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.96,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.10,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.02,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's a perfect crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.88,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When did you dig this hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:49.80,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You dug it yourself. You're not fooling anyone, Akechi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:52.94,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're taking it too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.94,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,????
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:51.74,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,They're playing {\i1}PCP...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.44,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.20,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe things are going too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:04.36,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been six years since we started writing for {\i1}Jack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:07.00,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,PCP is definitely popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.54,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We have a drama CD, and Azuki will be on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:13.02,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,When I write, I don't run out of ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:15.22,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I finish things more quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:18.30,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I have more time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:20.56,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But there are things we still need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:25.16,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We still haven't beaten {\i1}Crow...{\i0} or gotten an anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:26.98,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:30.86,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right. That's the important part!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:31.40,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:34.16,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:37.46,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are they rushing things?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:40.45,BakumanText,,0,0,0,,{\frz9.571\move(216,386,218,592,26,3321)}{\c&H565656&\3c&HECECEC&}TV Animation Proposal
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:48.06,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,The final script for the drama CD is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:49.44,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:51.92,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,He's got the characters down pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:55.00,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think Mai should have more lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.84,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,The crime itself though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.16,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:04.14,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,He's good with characters and dialog...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:08.58,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But he isn't as good as Takagi-kun\Nwhen it comes to inventing crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:09.34,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.92,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Ordinarily, we wouldn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:18.28,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though you're working on the manga,\Ncould you think of a crime for the drama CD?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.10,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:19.90,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:23.52,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll think of a crime for the drama CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:26.10,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I want it to be really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:28.30,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But... do you really have time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:32.82,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We're doing another series, so I have everything planned ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.52,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.52,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. Well good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:39.92,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Akito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:44.10,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that that series is done, shouldn't you be going to bed earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:46.74,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm working on the drama CD now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:48.98,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? The one Miho is going to be on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:49.46,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.26,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're writing a script for the drama CD?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:53.92,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm revising it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:58.28,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm making the actual crime parts more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:00.36,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Akito-san, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.52,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:05.80,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You've only just noticed my talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:10.38,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it. The fact that you can touch type is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:13.60,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaya-chan, guess what else I can do without looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:13.60,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Squee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:18.64,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Interesting... Are you sure this is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:21.16,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You could use this for the manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:23.48,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We want it to be as good as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:27.46,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,When people hear it, we want\Nthem to think PCP is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.88,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That way we'll be more likely to get an anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:34.34,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, while I'm here let's talk about the next series.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:35.60,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:38.14,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll get back to my pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:41.00,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We've already done two series with Akechi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.60,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,so I wanted to do something different for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.84,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:47.54,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, you've already got another idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:48.40,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:53.26,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:54.62,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:59.04,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, will Takagi-sensei be here tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:00.72,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:03.20,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to have him look at my storyboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.00,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.76,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You wrote something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.92,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But it isn't done yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:11.04,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad! I'm the only person\Nnot working on something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:12.84,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiratori-kun has a storyboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:15.04,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll come over now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:18.72,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,This is really interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.86,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,R-really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:24.06,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Rabuta doesn't trust people anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.70,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,And Peace can  read people's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.72,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's simple but well-constructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.88,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I love dogs so I thought that would\Nbe a good subject to write about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:35.22,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,His nose can tell the difference\Nbetween good and bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:37.84,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,And he can hear when people aren't being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:40.38,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,And when he licks someone, they tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.40,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,These are great ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:45.56,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But right now, it seems like the dog is the hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:47.26,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:52.06,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to be more suited for {\i1}Jack,{\i0}\Nyou need to make the hero stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:57.96,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a good idea, so revise it a bit\Nand we'll show it to Hattori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:01.32,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I want to get your okay first, Takagi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:04.42,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-san, if I ever draw something, please look at it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.40,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.82,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Shujin, you're pretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:13.54,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,In addition to the drama CD, {\i1}PCP{\i0} is getting a novelization!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:15.40,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,A novel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.76,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Tanabe Ikki-san will be writing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:21.96,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Of all the light-novel authors,\Nhe is the best for mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:24.10,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:28.30,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, we'll have you check his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:30.46,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the novelization okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:31.86,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:32.92,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.26,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,A drama CD... and a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.28,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Next will be an anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.44,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Anime again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.80,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to make it clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:44.60,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun. Mashiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:45.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.18,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}PCP{\i0} will not get an anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.76,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:51.58,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:55.88,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should say it's best to assume that it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:56.80,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:15:00.02,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We have a drama CD and a novel, why not an anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:02.62,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,The drama CD and novel are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:04.88,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,An anime is a big project.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.46,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.86,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't do it without a sponsor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:12.14,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}PCP{\i0} won't get a sponsor very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:13.72,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.26,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's popular! Kids love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:18.76,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We even saw kids playing it in the park!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:20.04,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:24.06,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,PCP has received complaint calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:28.10,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't shown you, but there are a lot of protest letters, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:30.00,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Children like to imitate the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:32.92,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Parents don't want their kids\Nimitating crimes and pranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:39.00,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't had them do anything actually\Nharmful, but people don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.04,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:44.16,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't like a battle manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:46.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You can actually do the stuff from the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:49.82,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But that difference is what makes it popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:50.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:55.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's realistic and totally possible. That is the manga's appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:59.18,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But for an anime, that would be a big flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:03.00,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we can change the nature of the crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:05.68,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Make them only do good things?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:07.42,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.52,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Saiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.96,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what makes it interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.06,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}PCP{\i0} is a popular manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:16.06,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:18.06,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Mashiro-kun is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:21.42,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,PCP is the perfect Ashirogi Muto manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:23.14,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's very popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:28.06,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun, you haven't done\Nanything wrong with the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:29.54,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:31.70,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But if we can't get an anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.96,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you so fixed on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:36.46,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's popular, isn't that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:40.18,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't get an anime, would\Nyou feel like you've failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:43.48,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,An anime is something that comes afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.42,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't something you plan for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:48.02,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.52,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Shujin, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:50.68,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:52.84,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori-san, let me be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:57.44,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,An anime... making a story that's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:59.46,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's our dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.50,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Every since middle school, when we teamed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:06.38,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We both want to see our manga become an anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.48,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's always been our goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:14.16,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,This may be harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:17.34,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun, you're the type to plan things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:20.82,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You've planned a lot for {\i1}PCP.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:23.80,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you really want an anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:27.66,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,you need to consider that in your planning too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:31.06,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Plan for the anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:34.64,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true... I didn't include that in my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:36.40,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:38.64,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Staying with {\i1}Jack...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:40.64,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Competing with Niizuma Eiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.08,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:44.58,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.82,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You never would have come up with this\Nmanga if you had planned for an anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:52.14,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But now that you've said this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:54.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,next time I'm going to plan\Nfor an anime from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.00,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Shujin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:57.96,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.98,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,PCP is a popular manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:01.66,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We should focus our effort on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:03.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We're only 20 after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.12,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,An anime isn't possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:09.40,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm a little shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:12.86,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't thinking about it at all. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:14.94,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:18.48,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,PCP owes its popularity to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:19.80,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Saiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:22.56,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you asked Azuki when she wants to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.58,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:26.20,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a big difference between 22 and 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.34,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know how long {\i1}PCP{\i0} will run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:32.34,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:40.22,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Azuki-san, when do you want to get married ideally?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.42,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't send this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.76,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't something I need to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:49.38,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}PCP{\i0} is doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:51.50,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But we haven't beaten {\i1}Crow{\i0} yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:54.96,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Eiji is writing two series.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.08,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But he does {\i1}Crow{\i0} by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:59.68,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,If Shujin and I both worked on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:02.82,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,A second series might put us ahead of Eiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:04.74,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,One more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:08.74,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Like Shujin said, if we specifically make it to be an anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:11.92,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We do both have a little more free time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:15.98,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I shouldn't tell Shujin something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.98,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to focus on {\i1}PCP.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.88,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I was the one who said we were only 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:26.12,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,We should see how things go, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:31.12,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,So right here is the focal point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.24,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You want a big full-page panel for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:34.90,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:37.30,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's about all I can help with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:39.12,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Your art...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:40.72,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Shujin does seem to have more free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:42.66,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't be long now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.20,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:45.82,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.86,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Before you head home, you\Ncan work on what I mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:49.74,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:53.18,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori-san is coming later.\NWant to have him look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:54.86,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:56.64,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Showing his storyboard to an editor...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.68,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I come too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:19:59.86,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.44,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,O-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:04.44,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys are all working hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.98,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Moriya-kun, let me have a look at yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.24,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:12.72,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think of my work?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:16.20,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I would have to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:19.02,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too complicated. It isn't {\i1}Jack{\i0} material.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:21.80,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,B-but kids nowadays...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:23.86,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Most importantly, it's difficult to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:27.00,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do the humans help the city grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.76,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,They don't have a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.58,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Readers don't want to be preached at.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.38,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,He's pretty tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:37.40,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to Shiratori-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:38.68,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.36,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:44.52,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,This is interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:45.42,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Interesting??
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:48.02,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:51.14,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever recognizes art.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.40,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,The dialog is pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:54.48,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:58.58,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,You could submit this to {\i1}Treasure...{\i0} no, even {\i1}Next.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.58,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That's awesome! Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:02.24,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Or is it too early for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:10.16,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori-san. I don't want to submit this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.16,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:14.20,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not? This is good enough to get serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.20,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is a good chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:18.20,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:21.54,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,This storyboard isn't really mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:23.70,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:25.96,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Before I showed it to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:29.42,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-sensei looked at it\Nand I revised it three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:30.40,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Three times?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:32.46,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:35.50,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he asked me to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:39.58,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it might be too good for a first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:41.34,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiratori-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:44.70,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you still have your original storyboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:45.82,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.94,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun is really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:54.86,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to show this to my superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:56.48,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But it will need to be marked:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:58.48,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,"Idea and art by Shiratori Shun"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:01.86,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,"Story by Ashirogi... no, Takagi Akito."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:04.00,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no good otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:09.50,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,, If it got serialized, it would be best\Nto have Takagi-kun write the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:12.58,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,If Shujin starts working on another series...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:14.72,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,But if that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:18.70,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun, you've just gotten used to writing PCP.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:23.78,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,So it wouldn't be right away, but would you think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:26.08,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:28.84,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be Mashiro's decision too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:30.84,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:32.46,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:39.76,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as it doesn't interfere with {\i1}PCP...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:41.28,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:58.39,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,When I struggle toward my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:23:02.94,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Those are the moments I love the most
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.31,0:23:07.57,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,I can feel our bond and will to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:12.16,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Our views overlap and electrify us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:16.74,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Let's improve ourselves, become what we should be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:21.83,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,You can see the future in our path
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:26.88,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,My comrades don't agree with me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:34.64,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Our pride clashes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:42.98,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,I can't let it go, I'll follow my heart from now on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:45.23,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,I'm prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:49.69,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,I'll charge right in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:52.86,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Unstoppable Pride
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:24:01.29,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,There's no other choice, this is what I love and this is what I'll do
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.58,0:24:06.25,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,I don't know what tomorrow will bring
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:09.21,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,But I know once again (just to get by),
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:11.88,BakumanKaraoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,We'll do our best
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.20,0:24:19.74,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,If I do my best, can I fulfill my dreams too?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.74,0:24:21.48,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:23.38,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't turn away from your true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.38,0:24:25.34,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time: Step and Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.34,0:24:28.24,BakumanDialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't give up on my dream!
